Organization Your packing organizers work like your drawers at home - you know what's in them so you can take out the relevant cube rather than rummaging through your suitcase and making a mess. The packing organizers allow for grouping items together in a variety of ways.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love these packing cubes!
reviews.reviewText: These colorful cubes are lightweight, flexible, and perfect for keeping suitcase in order. Love them!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent design and construction
reviews.reviewText: I highly recommend this product. This is my second purchase of Travelon's Packing Organizer set. I purchased these for organizing backpacks for my family's upcoming multi-week hike on the Camino de Santiago. The small and medium size are perfect for backpacking. All three sizes will be great for regular traveling.Surprisingly, these strong organizers are even lighter weight than the packing organizer set from a rival brand we used previously. I plan to bring a small pillowcase and transform the smallest one into a pillow at night.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great organizers - quality materials, three useful sizes and a see through mesh top
reviews.reviewText: These are great for travel - they organize and protect your clothes and the see through mesh top lets you quickly find what you need. The fabric is light and pliable but sturdy and the zippers operate smoothly. Three different sizes allow you to separate clothes by category and you can fit a lot in each one. These fit inside each other and store flat when you're not using them. A really useful and durable set for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 16, 2018
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice lightweight packing organizers
reviews.reviewText: These are very lightweight, well made, the piped edges help hold their shape, and they have handles. The contents are somewhat visible through the front mesh, but I think it's easier to rely on the separate colors to quickly identify what's packed in each one (which is why I bought Travelon, as other sets only came in one color). The zipper works well, but I wish it had two pulls. They are a good size for a small carry-on suitcase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Great I purchased a set years ago.The cubes are easy to use and keeps your clothes secure.When you arrive at your destination , you simply put the cubes in the drawers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 19, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Flexible, expandable, helps organize
reviews.reviewText: These were recommended by a friend and I used them for the first time on a weekend getaway with my husband. Perfect for smaller clothing items like underwear. When unpacking I simply unzipped each one, folded back the “lid” and put it in a drawer in the hotel room. So much easier than digging through the suitcase looking for the clean socks, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 24, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super cute organizers
reviews.reviewText: These are a great way to organize your things for travel and they are super cute.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: A little smaller than I imagined, but it gets the job done.

I bought this to travel and it is helping a lot during screenings at airports, and borders verifications, they can see easily what is inside, feel if something is hidden by touching it. When asked to take them out it is so easy to put everything back in your luggage with them.Not only this, but it keeps the clothes organized and protected.I had 1 for my underwears, 1 for my socks, and one for my tshirts. Only my jeans were loose in my luggage.The 3 different sizes are great to get various type of items organized.The zippers are sturdy. I still open them carefully knowing the fact, that with time they might break. But they feel sturdy and if not forced or used unproperly, they might last for a very long time.I recommand them so far, I will update if they deceive me with time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on December 11, 2023

reviews.reviewText: I have several different brands of packing cubes. I like these ones because they are a bit stiffer. They work well for charging cords, journals, card games, medicine, etc.I have six different sizes and use them all the time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on July 12, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I was impressed with the first set I bought so purchased a second set. Well made and makes packing tidier and easier.

reviews.reviewTitle: Light-weight, versatile, expandable. Very happy with them.
reviews.reviewText: These cubes expand amazingly and hold much more than you would think. You can see through the mesh to see what each contains. They are smallish but perfect, because I combine them with a larger set of cubes as well. (I have since bought a 3rd set). I love the way my clothes, items are each in their own space. Saves time with trying to find things in my luggage, which frustrates me hugely! :)
